comments: Instructor: Christian Tschudi  Great speaker, great relationship with students, clearly committed to making this a valuable exercise for the students

Instructor: Christian Tschudi  Dr. Tschudi offered a realistic and relevant perspective in addition to the course material presented in the class. I felt very comfortable asking Dr. Tschudi questions.
